===Etymology===
Greek δοκέω [dokeō], "to seem"
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#{{Christianity}} A [[heresy]] that maintains Jesus only appeared to have a physical body. Notwithstanding the Christian view, this is precisely the Muslim view. The belief has certain motifs in common with [[gnosticism]] and [[monophysitism]]. 

